Meaning:
のける【退ける】
1. to put something out of the way, to move (something, someone) aside
2. to set aside, to keep apart
3. to remove (someone) from the group, to shun
4. to do well despite difficulties, to accomplish despite adversity
5. to do resolutely, to do boldly

2. serving, helping, course
3. kanji radical 108 (at the bottom)

せつめいかい【説明会】 ★★
information session, briefing, explanatory meeting

ようそ【要素】 ★★★
1. component, factor, item (e.g. in list)
2. element (e.g. in array), member (e.g. data structure)

がくげいかい【学芸会】 ★★
school arts festival
